ruby game_master.rb -H 
Usage: Simulate Powerball Lottery

Options
    -N  number_of_simulated_games,   Provide number of games you want simulated.
        --simulated_games
    -B  number_of_white_balls_match, Provide number of white balls match to consider a win.
        --white_balls_match
    -R, --red_ball_match             Flag for whether red ball should be matched to consider a win.
    -H, --help                       Show this message
